Package: inflection
Type: Package
Title: Finds the Inflection Point of a Curve
Version: 1.3.7
Date: 2025-07-17
Authors@R: person("Demetris T.", "Christopoulos", email = "dchristop@econ.uoa.gr", role = c("aut", "cre")) 
